_sText:
This is my first map I've out on banana.nu, so go easy ;). O've only been mapping for a few weeks now, and this is the best map I've made in my opinion. Both teams start either side of the long bridge in a castle, and fight from castle to castle (or rush if they're brave :)

This map is mainly for snipers but other weapons can be used if the player is up for a challenge.
